00:45:08.800 --> 00:45:11.980
that's happening and you're
redefining your sense of self

00:45:11.980 --> 00:45:14.920
and your priorities and
having all these paradigm

00:45:14.920 --> 00:45:20.260
shifts with those that are
close to you who are not

00:45:20.260 --> 00:45:21.760
on this journey
with you if you're

00:45:21.760 --> 00:45:23.140
doing it as a personal thing?

00:45:25.910 --> 00:45:28.160
Have you had
experiences where you

00:45:28.160 --> 00:45:31.182
had to reconcile with
that in certain ways?

00:45:31.182 --> 00:45:33.140
How do you bring your
loved ones along with you

00:45:33.140 --> 00:45:35.870
on the journey or whatever?

00:45:35.870 --> 00:45:38.360
NIRALI SHAH: I can just
say to my own experience

00:45:38.360 --> 00:45:42.830
is that at some point,
it was not easy.

00:45:42.830 --> 00:45:46.850
At some point, at
the time, my parents

00:45:46.850 --> 00:45:50.100
could not understand what
I'm doing with my life.

00:45:50.100 --> 00:45:55.190
And I feel like I had to just
go through that, at least

00:45:55.190 --> 00:45:57.470
in my case, because I knew.

00:45:57.470 --> 00:46:00.350
I had a sense of
what I was doing.

00:46:00.350 --> 00:46:02.360
It was not completely
clear at the time,

00:46:02.360 --> 00:46:04.700
but there was still
a deep calling.

00:46:04.700 --> 00:46:07.040
And I knew that I had
to be true to that.

00:46:09.640 --> 00:46:13.730
And yeah, it was kind
of rocky at that time.

00:46:13.730 --> 00:46:18.270
And now, all these
years later, they

00:46:18.270 --> 00:46:24.320
have deep respect and
love and gratitude for me

00:46:24.320 --> 00:46:26.650
and for the path I have chosen.

00:46:26.650 --> 00:46:29.850
And they are
incredibly supportive.

00:46:29.850 --> 00:46:36.080
So I wish I could have taken
them with me at that time.

00:46:36.080 --> 00:46:38.080
But that was not happening.

00:46:38.080 --> 00:46:42.530
And I saw that also as
a part of my practice,

00:46:42.530 --> 00:46:47.060
that how this is
shaping my truth

00:46:47.060 --> 00:46:49.640
or my faith in this practice.

00:46:49.640 --> 00:46:50.960
AUDIENCE: Hello.

