Or do you feel like we
should try to get people?

00:47:09.350 --> 00:47:11.890
NIRALI SHAH: [LAUGHS] We should?

00:47:11.890 --> 00:47:12.860
How do you mean that?

00:47:12.860 --> 00:47:14.630
AUDIENCE: So should
we try to get people

00:47:14.630 --> 00:47:16.040
to be part of the revolution?

00:47:16.040 --> 00:47:19.360
Or should we let them be?

00:47:19.360 --> 00:47:22.560
If they want to be
