00:47:22.560 --> 00:47:25.670
should we try to get them to?

00:47:25.670 --> 00:47:34.110
So it's like should you
convince people to meditate,

00:47:34.110 --> 00:47:35.340
to do like--

00:47:37.400 --> 00:47:39.650
NIRALI SHAH: It's actually
a very meaningful question,

00:47:39.650 --> 00:47:40.483
what are you asking.

00:47:40.483 --> 00:47:45.040
I can see the subtlety
