00:47:45.040 --> 00:47:46.580
Because obviously,
you're not seeing

00:47:46.580 --> 00:47:48.770
that we should try to
force people to meditate.

00:47:48.770 --> 00:47:50.330
I know you're not asking that.

00:47:50.330 --> 00:47:52.160
So there's a nuance
to your question.

