00:52:20.280 --> 00:52:23.182
Monday nights is a
good place to start,

00:52:23.182 --> 00:52:26.910
where there would be
sit and a Dharma talk.

00:52:26.910 --> 00:52:32.580
And I think there is SIY
here, Search Inside Yourself,

00:52:32.580 --> 00:52:33.780
at Google.

00:52:33.780 --> 00:52:36.990
And they also offer
the introduction

00:52:36.990 --> 00:52:40.540
