meditation practice.

00:52:40.540 --> 00:52:44.190
And then if you
feel so inclined,

00:52:44.190 --> 00:52:46.620
there are these ten-day
meditation retreats

00:52:46.620 --> 00:52:48.990
by SN Goenka.

00:52:48.990 --> 00:52:54.110
I personally recommend
Spirit Rock as well,

00:52:54.110 --> 00:52:55.440
which is in Marin.

00:52:55.440 --> 00:52:57.000
And they have a lot of retreats.

00:52:57.000 --> 00:53:00.660
I would check out some
of those websites.

